author: jonm
msg: HTTPCLIENT-1073: caching module need not be a stickler about receiving
a 407 (Proxy Authentication Required) response without a Proxy-Authenticate
header and should pass it through to local client. (backport of r1084590

author: jonm
msg: Minor enhancement to stale-while-revalidate (RFC5861) handling; now we can
also serve stale 304s (Not Modified) while asynchronously revalidating. Prior
to this, we were always returning a stale 200 response regardless of whether
the incoming request was conditional or not. The old behavior was not
incorrect, but this is better. (backport of r1080422,r1080575 from trunk)
